5:
God, when we pray to you, you answer us and save us by doing awesome deeds;\q2 you are the one who rescues us;
\q1 people who live in very remote places on the earth, on the other side of the oceans, trust in you.


\q1

7:
You are the one who calms the seas when they roar,\q2 and stop the waves from pounding on the shore;
\q1 you also calm people when they cause a lot of trouble.


\q1
